transition between
administrations.

14:27.900 --> 14:31.938 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I began by asking him just how
smoothly the
transition to the Trump team is
going.

14:31.971 --> 14:35.575 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN KERRY, U.S. Secretary of
State: Well,
it's going pretty smoothly
because there's

14:35.608 --> 14:37.744 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
