14:37.777 --> 14:41.781 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
There are some people that have
been in the
building for a period of time.

14:41.814 --> 14:49.055 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But, you know, quite candidly, I
think there
has not been a lot of high-level
exchange

14:49.088 --> 14:50.590 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
at this point in time.

14:50.623 --> 14:56.295 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
