44:06.077 --> 44:08.079 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And so it's fitting that he
would be here.

44:08.112 --> 44:11.415 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Annette
Gordon-Reed, thank
you very much.

44:11.449 --> 44:12.650 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
