so that we
provided a model for them, but
they love it.

46:36.060 --> 46:41.098 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Samantha King
works for KID
smART, a consulting company
that's helped

46:41.132 --> 46:44.001 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
