be used not
just as a flower, something to
do after math

47:23.174 --> 47:27.211 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and science scores are up, but
actually as
a reform strategy, something
that really can

47:27.244 --> 47:29.947 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
help to reach and teach and
engage children.

47:29.980 --> 47:34.118 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Turnaround Arts
is a 5-year-old
program created by the
President's Committee

47:34.151 --> 47:36.020 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
on the Arts and Humanities.

47:36.053 --> 47:41.492 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's the first federal effort to
use arts
education as a tool to boost
achievement in

47:41.525 --> 47:46.831 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
