body.

49:16.220 --> 49:21.091 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Woodard, known
for award-winning
film, stage and television
roles, is a veteran

49:21.125 --> 49:22.426 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
of the program.

49:22.459 --> 49:23.561 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Why is this work important?

49:23.594 --> 49:26.397 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ALFRE WOODARD: Somebody showed
up for both
of us.

49:26.430 --> 49:30.301 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
That's why we're here.

49:30.334 --> 49:35.940 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
