it completes the human being,
our ability

49:35.973 --> 49:39.476 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to create, and to express that
creation.

49:39.510 --> 49:45.249 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we also have all the visuals
now of channels
in your brain opening up when
you're doing

49:45.282 --> 49:46.750 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
a particular discipline.

49:46.784 --> 49:51.121 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, once we had that, we wanted
to come into
schools, put it to the test.

49:51.155 --> 49:57.127 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GRAHAM NASH: You know, this
particular school,
it was one of their very first
projects.

49:57.161 --> 50:01.866 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
